<p style="text-align: left; margin-left: 36pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Palatino Linotype'; font-size: medium;">Dear LFDCS Families,</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left; margin-left: 36pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Palatino Linotype'; font-size: medium;">Lawrence Family Devlopment will be closed for the remainder of the school year. Remote learning will continue though Monday, June 22, 2020, LFDCS's 185th day of school which is required by the Massachusetts Department of Secondary and Elementary Education. Summer Academy will not be held this year.</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left; margin-left: 36pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Palatino Linotype'; font-size: medium;">K-1 through Grade 3 parents and students can access at-home resources on this webpage. At the top right of this page, scroll over to Resources and scroll down to Online Programs and click on Clever. Grades 4-8 parents and students can access at-home resources through Schoology. </span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left; margin-left: 36pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Palatino Linotype'; font-size: medium;">We appreciate your patience and flexibility during this fluid situation and will continue to communicate with you through Zoom, AP Notify, email and on this website. </span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left; margin-left: 36pt;"><b><span style="font-family: 'Palatino Linotype'; font-size: medium;" size="3" linotype="linotype" face="face">Please click the Google Translate button in the top right corner of the website to read in Spanish.</span></b></p>
<p style="text-align: left; margin-left: 36pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Palatino Linotype'; font-size: medium;">Sincerely,</span></strong></p>
